    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActiveCellChangedEvent, ActiveSelectionChangedEvent, AllBordersColorChangedEvent, AllBordersLineTypeChangedEvent, BackgroundColorChangedEvent, FontBoldChangedEvent, FontColorChangedEvent, FontDoubleUnderlineChangedEvent, FontItalicChangedEvent, FontNameChangedEvent, FontSizeChangedEvent, FontStrokeEventChanged, FontUnderlineChangedEvent, FontVerticalShiftingChangedEvent, ForegroundAccentColorChangedEvent, GridVisibilityChangedEvent, HorizontalAlignmentChangedEvent, ReadOnlyModeChangedEvent, TextRotationChangedEvent, VerticalAlignmentChangedEvent, WorkbookProtectionStateChangedEvent

    public abstract class AbstractDataEvent<TData>
extends Object
    The main class of all API-supported events.

    There are two kinds of API-events:

    1. The ones that have '...ChangedEvent' at the end of the name. They inform about the changes of the internal states

    2. The ones that have '...Request' at the end of the name. They are responsible for the UI control performance of the corresponding operation

    See Also:
    ActiveSelectionChangedEvent
